text.section:
As used in this section, "bottle club" means any club:
That serves, sells, gives, or dispenses alcoholic beverages to its members or guests;
That keeps for its members or guests any alcoholic beverages;
Allows to be consumed by its members or guests on its premises any alcoholic beverages that have been reserved or purchased by the members or guests;
At which patrons are served, given, or allowed to consume alcoholic beverages after legal closing hours from the supplies that the patrons have previously purchased or reserved; or
That sells, dispenses, serves, keeps, or allows to be consumed any setups or other component parts of mixed alcoholic drinks to its members or guests.
